        <abstract> 
<p>Before JDH discusses flora of Canary Islands CD suggests he read F. B. White’s paper [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">11707</hi>], which explains stocking of Atlantic island fauna as due to changed currents during [last, or Miocene] northern glacial period.</p> 
